      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "andi@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:00"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "Andi Bailey",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "andi@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:02"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "Andi Bailey",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "andi@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "Well, I guess, like, that's a good pivot to talking about a time when you've had to work through conflicting priorities between teams to complete a deliverable.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:03"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:18"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "Often, you know, often kind of in the startup world, it's going to be budget related.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:19"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "When you have something you need tomorrow and maybe it's not in your budget or your manpower might be down, something like that.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:26"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "And, uh, there it's finding out kind of, kind of ranking your priorities, what needs to be done?",
    "timestamp": "00:08:36"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "What would you like to be done?",
    "timestamp": "00:08:43"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "And what's just sort of nice to have finding out what, uh, and then from there finding out what's approachable and what isn't, um, because you're setting goals that really are unattainable.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:44"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "You're sort of just, uh, I would say we're wasting everyone.",
    "timestamp": "00:08:57"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "It's time, but a little bit, I guess.",
