  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "Andi Bailey",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "andi@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "Do you have an example?",
    "timestamp": "00:09:06"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "Yeah, let me think of, I guess, in the product side right now, what I'm going through at Energybox, we've had the same customer request come in maybe a dozen times, and our product team really doesn't have the bandwidth to change our platform in the way that we need it to.",
    "timestamp": "00:09:08"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "So we're working through a couple of ideas right now to get them really smaller goals of one or two things, like can we add this widget, can we add these reporting tools, can we maybe pilot it with someone and see if it works.",
    "timestamp": "00:09:27"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "And that way we continue to move the ball forward without letting it lose momentum, but also make it a way where it's realistic for the development team to keep up as well.",
    "timestamp": "00:09:43"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "Andi Bailey",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "andi@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "Okay, um, how do",
