  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "Yeah, I mean, it's, I guess you'd want to solve, you'd want to start with the ones that are going to make, I mean, make the largest difference first, guess the kind of cheesy way of saying it, but.",
    "timestamp": "00:10:10"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "Andi Bailey",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": "andi@growthx.ai"
    },
    "text": "Measure that.",
    "timestamp": "00:10:24"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "Yeah, exactly.",
    "timestamp": "00:10:25"
  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "Ones that'll have, make, make an operational change, make life easier, and ones that'll be sustainable.",
