  },
  {
    "speaker": {
      "display_name": "brianfogg",
      "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
    },
    "text": "But, so, yeah, I mean, the ones that are going to change how you work and can change the larger operational workflow will take precedence over some of the smaller projects.",
